TITLE: Import Zod from Velite (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to import the Zod library through the 'velite' package.  It re-exports Zod's functionality, making it available for use within Velite projects. `z` can then be used to create schema definitions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zce/velite/blob/main/docs/guide/velite-schemas.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { z } from 'velite'

// `z` is re-export of Zod
```

