TITLE: Using s.mdx() to Parse MDX Content (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: The `s.mdx(options)` schema parses MDX content and returns the function-body of the component. Options include `gfm`, `removeComments`, and `copyLinkedFiles`.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zce/velite/blob/main/docs/guide/velite-schemas.md#_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
code: s.mdx()
// => function-body
```

