TITLE: Using timestamp schema in collection (TS)
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the `timestamp` schema within a Velite collection definition. It showcases integration into the `schema` property of the `defineCollection` function, assigning it to the `lastModified` field.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zce/velite/blob/main/docs/guide/last-modified.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const posts = defineCollection({
  // ...
  schema: {
    // ...
    lastModified: timestamp()
  }
})
```

