TITLE: Markdown & MDX Processing (Velite)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to transform the content body from markdown to HTML using `s.markdown()` within a Velite collection schema. Alternatively, `s.mdx()` can be used for MDX processing.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zce/velite/blob/main/docs/guide/define-collections.md#_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
const posts = defineCollection({
  schema: s.object({
    content: s.markdown() // or s.mdx()
  })
})
```

