TITLE: Configuring @shikijs/rehype in velite.config.js
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript code configures Velite to use @shikijs/rehype for syntax highlighting with the 'nord' theme. It imports the necessary modules and defines a Velite configuration object with rehypePlugins specified.
