TITLE: Defining VeliteFile Class in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Defines the `VeliteFile` class, which extends the `VFile` class and provides methods for accessing parsed records, file content, mdast/hast objects, plain text, and meta objects. It also includes static methods for retrieving and creating `VeliteFile` instances. This class is used to represent and manage files within the Velite project.
