DESCRIPTION: Defines the `Loader` interface for file loaders. It specifies properties for the loader's name (`name`), a regular expression to test file types (`test`), and a `load` function that takes a VFile object and returns an entry or an array of entries. This interface is used to create custom file loaders within the Velite project.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zce/velite/blob/main/docs/reference/types.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
/**
 * File loader
 */
interface Loader {
  /**
   * Loader name
   * @description
   * The same name will overwrite the built-in loader,
   * built-in loaders: 'json', 'yaml', 'matter'
   */
  name: string
  /**
   * File test regexp
   * @example
   * /\.md$/
   */
  test: RegExp
  /**
   * Load file content
   * @param file vfile
   * @returns entry or entries
   */
  load: (file: VFile) => Promisable<Entry | Entry[]>
}
```

